it.dc.bridge.om

Interface CoAPResponseMessage

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ResponseMessage

    public interface CoAPResponseMessage
    The CoAP response message interface. The class that represents a response message implements this interface and all methods it contains.

    The following methods are implemented:

    • getCode() get the response code
    • setCode(CoAP.ResponseCode) set the response code
    • getOptions() get the option fields
    • setOptions(Options) set the option fields
    • getPayload() get the message payload
    • getPayloadString() get the message payload as a string
    • setPayload(byte[]) set the message payload from raw data
    • setPayload(String) set the message payload from a string
    See Also:
    CoAPRequestMessage
